---
title: Chipotle Chorizo & Spinach Rice Bowl with Cheddar, Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Savor the bold flavours of our Chipotle Chorizo & Spinach Rice Bowl, where mild chorizo meets smoky chipotle. Paired with fluffy
spinach rice and a charred corn salsa, this bowl is a hearty and satisfying combination that is sure to please.
